# Readme

This image allows deploying a ```nginx``` to serve Marquez user authenticated requests.
It authenticates requests via [`vouch`](../vouch/README.md) that must be run on port 9090.
The resources are served by [`caddy`](../caddy/README.md) that must be run on port 9091.
The three components must be deployed as a pod in kubernetes communicating via localhost with each other.
The purpose of this solution is to allow serving Marquez's requests.
Okta (via vouch) is used to authenticate users.